{
  "texts": [
    "We recruited 400 from prolific.",
    "We ended up recruiting 397 participants as 3 did not complete the survey.",
    "Based on our exclusion criteria we removed 5 participants for providing nonsensical responses and 6 participants who missed our 3 attention checks.",
    "Our final sample was therefore 386 (178 women, 207 men, 1 another gender/none; age: M = 40.58, SD = 12.95), with 186 assigned to the human partner condition and 200 to the AI partner condition.",
    "Participants signed in to the study, and received a reappraisal training, similar to that of Study 1."
  ]
}